<HEADLINE> France Wins Title of Euro 2000 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROTTERDAM, July 2 (Xinhua) -- Italy won the title of the
European Championship after defeating Italy 2-1 at extra time in
Rotterdam, the Netherlands on Sunday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
