<HEADLINE> Results of Final between France and Italy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Italy: 12-Francesco Toldo; 5-Fabio Cannavaro, 13-Alessandro
Nesta, 15-Mark Iuliano, 3-Paolo Maldini (captain); 11-Gianluca
Pessotto, 14-Luigi Di Biagio (16-Massimo Ambrosini 65),4-Demetrio
Albertini, 18-Stefano Fiore (10-Alessandro Del Piero 53); 20-
Francesco Totti, 21-Marco Delvecchio (19-Vicenzo Montella 85).
</P>
<P>
Referee: Anders Frisk (Sweden)
</P>
