<HEADLINE> Angola Satisfied With Results of Lusaka Meeting </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, July 3 (Xinhua) -- Angolan Interior Minister Fernando
da Piedade Monday expressed his satisfaction with the results of
the Lusaka meeting, during which a supervising mechanism was
created to monitor the security situation along the
Angolan-Zambian border.
