<HEADLINE> Manila Stocks End Slightly Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, July 3 (Xinhua) -- Share prices in the Philippine
Stocks Exchange managed to close slightly higher Monday amid a
lack of market-moving news to spur market activity.
</P>
