Analysts said the market still maintained to keep at the 1500-
level despite negative news in the market.
</P>
<P>
"It is fortunate that the market is still keeping in the 1,500
range. However, we should not discount that the market will
continue to be threatened if more negative news appear," an
analyst at a local bank said. 
