<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Open Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 3 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks gained 21.28
points, or 0.13 percent, to open at 16,177.06 Monday.
</P>
<P>
The Hang Seng Index dropped 131.02 points, or 0.80 percent, to
close at 16,155.78 Friday. 
</P>
