from(EU) national states to constructing a rapid reaction force
which was decided upon in December 1999. We also hope to prepare
for an agreement aimed at making up the insufficiencies in terms
of technology,'' he said.
</P>
<P>
He said that Europe is expected to have by 2003 a force which
can fulfil the mission of interfering or reestablishing peace in ``
a European theater or that close to Europe.''
</P>
<P>
``Our objective is to be able to deploy in 60 days, for a
period of at least one year, a corps of army with from 50,000 to
60,000 men,'' said the defense minister. 
