<HEADLINE> Chile Invests 552 Million Dollars Abroad </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It should be indicated that between April and June of year 2000,
the lowest three monthly period in the last six years was
verified, which is below the 130 million dollars obtained during
1999's same period, when the country experienced full economic
crisis.
</P>
